      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>You’ve modified the ends of your LFAN to tighten their grip.</p>\n<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.feats.Item.pBDeKG9AUxoDn8mo]{Pincered LFAN}</p><hr /><p><strong>Benefit:</strong> You gain a +2 species bonus to your KAC against disarm combat maneuvers. You can use your @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.racial-features.Item.oqsObKnxzFKUOb5u]{LFAN} to grapple other creatures. When you score a critical hit with your LFAN natural weapon, you can also automatically grapple the target if your attack roll equals or exceeds the target’s KAC +4 (pinning them instead if your attack roll equals or exceeds the target’s KAC +13).</p>\n<p><em>Enable/disable modifiers in the Modifiers tab.</em></p>"
